  <brief_title>Study of the Use of Humidified Warmed Gas and the Effect on Post-Operative Pain in Laparoscopic Cholecystectomies</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomised Controlled Trail of Warmed Humidified Insufflation Versus Cold Non-Humidified Insufflation in Elective Laparoscopic Cholecystectomies: Does This Reduce Post-Operative Pain?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Pennine Acute Hospitals NHS Trust</agency>
