  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Double blind RCT comparing elective laparoscopic cholecystectomy using warmed, humidified gas
      (new) against laparoscopic cholecystectomy with cool, dry gas (usual). Sample size of 200
      patients. Outcome measures are postoperative opiate analgesia use, and post operative
      numerical pain scores.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
